  "texts": [
    "However, other studies have pointed out that although music affected driving performance and reaction times, it had no significant effect on subjective emotion levels [168].",
    "Empathetic speech requires empathetic adaptation of the in-vehicle voice agent's speech output to adapt to the emotional state of drivers and occupants in the driving environment.",
    "Studies on empathetic speech revealed that the matched speech arousal level could have a positive impact on driving performance and the frequency of interactions [175,179].",
    "Besides, the empathetic speech was liked by drivers, and could decrease the impact of sadness and anger on driving [170].",
    "Empathetic speech may be a suitable method to regulate the driver's negative emotions."
  ],
